    <item>
      <title>交易员仍预计美联储将很快实施至少两次大规模降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/traders-still-see-at-least-two-jumbo-fed-cuts-coming-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国利率期权市场的交易员仍押注美联储今年将至少进行一次超大规模降息——只是可能不会在 11 月 5 日美国大选之前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/traders-still-see-at-least-two-jumbo-fed-cuts-coming-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 21:15:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Corebridge 预计替代资产的长期回报率为 8% 至 9%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/corebridge-expects-long-term-return-on-alternatives-of-8-to-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Corebridge Financial Inc. 首席执行官凯文霍根 (Kevin Hogan) 表示，他预计该公司 55 亿美元的另类投资组合将产生 8% 至 9% 的长期收益，尽管最近几个季度未能达到这一目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/corebridge-expects-long-term-return-on-alternatives-of-8-to-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 21:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行削减债券购买规模，为日本投资者创造条件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/boj-s-bond-buying-cuts-carve-out-opening-for-japanese-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日本央行放缓债务购买步伐，本地投资者却采取相反举措，限制了债券收益率的上行压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/boj-s-bond-buying-cuts-carve-out-opening-for-japanese-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普媒体期权成本随大选飙升，禁售期即将结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/trump-media-options-costs-soar-with-election-lockup-end-looming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员们为选举相关的波动和内幕交易禁售期的结束做准备，唐纳德·特朗普媒体公司的股票期权成本已飙升至自 3 月份首次开始交易以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/trump-media-options-costs-soar-with-election-lockup-end-looming</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 20:53:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默多克旗下 REA 开始与英国房地产门户网站 Rightmove 进行收购谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/murdoch-s-rea-said-to-start-takeover-talks-with-uk-s-rightmove</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，澳大利亚房地产上市提供商 REA Group Ltd. 已向 Rightmove Plc 提出初步收购提议，几天前该公司确认了对英国市值最大的房地产门户网站的收购意向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/murdoch-s-rea-said-to-start-takeover-talks-with-uk-s-rightmove</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗挥霍委内瑞拉美元储备，政权面临新威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/venezuela-maduro-blows-through-dollar-stockpile-in-new-threat-to-regime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从宣布自己赢得七月总统选举以来，委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗就遭到了世界各国政府的谴责、大规模街头抗议的攻击和一些最亲密的盟友的唾弃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/venezuela-maduro-blows-through-dollar-stockpile-in-new-threat-to-regime</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待美国通胀数据，拉丁美洲外汇表现不及同行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/emerging-currencies-weaken-for-second-day-as-stocks-halt-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周三美国关键通胀数据公布前全球市场普遍存在避险情绪，拉丁美洲货币周二表现落后于新兴市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/emerging-currencies-weaken-for-second-day-as-stocks-halt-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:36:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与哈里斯辩论期间，股票、债券和货币投资者关注的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/edgy-traders-gird-for-potentially-pivotal-trump-harris-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯与前总统唐纳德·特朗普首次举行总统辩论之前，投资者正在权衡选举风险，他们的紧张情绪已经比 6 月份特朗普与其曾经的对手总统乔·拜登在舞台上会面之前高涨得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/edgy-traders-gird-for-potentially-pivotal-trump-harris-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管“大银行悲观”，但股市仍获得科技股提振：市场综述</title>
